description: Available at https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Geoffrey demonstrates specialized techniques used in his version of the Scottish folk song "My Love is Like a Red Red Rose", from his latest solo album Heart of the Piano (2013 - Motéma). Topics include "backphrasing" (thinking like a singer), orchestration concepts (call-and-response or dialogue between the left and right hand), and sound effects including his unique "ocean waves" sound. Includes a PDF of the complete note-for-note transcription from the recording. (Level: Advanced)
